    <entry>
      <title>typescript加载声音文件</title>
      <link href="2021/05/19/typescript%E5%8A%A0%E8%BD%BD%E5%A3%B0%E9%9F%B3%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6/"/>
      <url>2021/05/19/typescript%E5%8A%A0%E8%BD%BD%E5%A3%B0%E9%9F%B3%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="typescript加载声音文件"><a href="#typescript加载声音文件" class="headerlink" title="typescript加载声音文件"></a>typescript加载声音文件</h1><h3 id="过程"><a href="#过程" class="headerlink" title="过程"></a>过程</h3><p>使用js的时候,如果要引入声音文件,可以使用<code>import sound from './sound/a.wav'</code>,但是在ts里面就会报错”找不到模块….”</p><p>了解到有一个包<code>types/node</code>,可以用来解决这个问题,安装之后打开<code>node_modules/@types/node</code>下有个index.d.ts文件,在index.d.ts文件末尾添加如下代码</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs js">declare <span class="hljs-built_in">module</span> <span class="hljs-string">'*.wav'</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>这样就可以使用import引入声音文件,但这样只能是ts不报错,webpack打包却过不了</p><p><img src="/2021/05/19/typescript%E5%8A%A0%E8%BD%BD%E5%A3%B0%E9%9F%B3%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6/image-20210519134605274.png" alt="image-20210519134605274"></p><h3 id="webpack打包声音文件"><a href="#webpack打包声音文件" class="headerlink" title="webpack打包声音文件"></a>webpack打包声音文件</h3><p>安装<code>file-loader</code>(对于小文件可以使用<code>url-loader</code>转换成base64), 配置webpack.config.js</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs js">npm i -D file-loader<br><span class="hljs-comment">// 配置webpack.config.js</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">rules</span>: [<br>  {<br>    <span class="hljs-attr">test</span>: <span class="hljs-regexp">/\.(mp4|webm|ogg|mp3|wav|flac|aac)(\?.*)?$/</span>,<br>    loader: <span class="hljs-string">"file-loader"</span><br>  }<br>]<br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h3 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h3><p>同样的引入其他文件,也可以使用这个方法,例如<code>json</code>,<code>image</code></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> typescript </tag>
            
            <tag> module </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>webpack打包ts代码</title>
      <link href="2021/05/16/webpack%E6%89%93%E5%8C%85ts%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81/"/>
      <url>2021/05/16/webpack%E6%89%93%E5%8C%85ts%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="使用步骤"><a href="#使用步骤" class="headerlink" title="使用步骤"></a>使用步骤</h2><ol><li><p>使用webpack需要安装模块,所以需要有package.json文件这样才可以使用npm</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs js">npm init -y<br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></li><li><p>安装webpack,typescript开发依赖包,运行命令结束需要看一下package.json中的开发依赖有没有安装的几个模块</p>  <figure class="highlight js"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs js">npm i -D webpack webpack-cli typescript typescript-loader<br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></li><li><p>创建webpack.config.js文件,配置webpack</p> <figure class="highlight js"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs js"><span class="hljs-comment">// 引入path库,用于处理路径</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> path = <span class="hljs-built_in">require</span>(<span class="hljs-string">'path'</span>)<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// webpack中所有的配置信息都应该写在module.exports中</span><br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">module</span>.exports = {<br><br>  <span class="hljs-comment">// 指定入口文件</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">entry</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"./src/index.ts"</span>,<br>  <span class="hljs-comment">// 指定打包所在目录</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">output</span>: {<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 指定打包文件的目录</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">path</span>: path.resolve(__dirname, <span class="hljs-string">'dist'</span>),<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 打包后文件的文件名</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">filename</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"bundle.js"</span><br>  },<br>  <span class="hljs-comment">// 指定webpack打包时要使用的模块</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">module</span>: {<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 指定要加载的规则</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">rules</span>: [<br>      {<br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// 规则生效的文件</span><br>        <span class="hljs-attr">test</span>: <span class="hljs-regexp">/\.ts$/</span>,<br>        use: <span class="hljs-string">'ts-loader'</span>,<br>        <span class="hljs-attr">exclude</span>: <span class="hljs-regexp">/node_modules/</span><br>      }<br>    ]<br>  }<br><br>}<br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></li><li><p>修改package.json,在其中加入webpack的运行命令</p><p> <img src="/2021/05/16/webpack%E6%89%93%E5%8C%85ts%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81/image-20210516152821095.png" alt="image-20210516152821095"></p></li><li><p>ts需要在html中运行,还需要配置webapck的html插件<br> 安装html-webpack-plugin</p> <figure class="highlight js"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs js">npm i -D html-webpack-plugin<br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p> 修改webpack.config.js</p> <figure class="highlight js"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs js"><span class="hljs-comment">// 引入html插件</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> HTMLWebpackPlugin = <span class="hljs-built_in">require</span>(<span class="hljs-string">'html-webpack-plugin'</span>)<br><span class="hljs-comment">// 添加plugin选项</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">plugins</span>: [<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> HTMLWebpackplugin({<br>      <span class="hljs-comment">//title: "自定义title",</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">template</span>:<span class="hljs-string">"./src/index.html"</span><br>  }),<br>]<br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></li><li><p>安装webpack-dev-server开发服务器</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs js">npm i -D webpack-dev-server<br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>修改package.json的”scripts”</p><p><img src="/2021/05/16/webpack%E6%89%93%E5%8C%85ts%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81/image-20210516154301221.png" alt="image-20210516154301221"></p></li><li><p>安装clean-webpack-plugin插件</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs js">npm i -D clean-webpack-plugin<br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>修改webpack.config.js</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs js"><span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> {CleanWebpackPlugin} = <span class="hljs-built_in">require</span>(<span class="hljs-string">'clean-webpack-plugin'</span>)<br><span class="hljs-attr">plugins</span>: [<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> CleanWebpackPlugin(),<br>]<br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></li><li><p>设置模块引用扩展名</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs js"><span class="hljs-comment">// webpack.config.js</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">resolve</span>: {<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 在ts文件可以使用import引入的文件后缀</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">extensions</span>: [<span class="hljs-string">'.ts'</span>, <span class="hljs-string">'.js'</span>]<br>}<br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></li><li><p>引入babel,解决兼容性问题</p><p>安装babel的包</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs js">npm i -D @babel/core @babel/preset-env babel-loader core-js@<span class="hljs-number">3</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>修改webpack.config.js</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs js"><span class="hljs-built_in">module</span>: {<br> <span class="hljs-attr">rules</span>: [<br>      {<br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// 规则生效的文件</span><br>        <span class="hljs-attr">test</span>: <span class="hljs-regexp">/\.ts$/</span>,<br>        use: [<br>          <span class="hljs-comment">// 编译的顺序从下往上</span><br>          { <span class="hljs-comment">// 配置babel</span><br>            <span class="hljs-comment">// 指定加载器</span><br>            <span class="hljs-attr">loader</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"babel-loader"</span>,<br>            <span class="hljs-comment">// 设置babel兼容环境</span><br>            <span class="hljs-attr">options</span>: {<br>              <span class="hljs-comment">// 预定义环境</span><br>              <span class="hljs-attr">presets</span>: [<br>                [<br>                  <span class="hljs-comment">// 指定环境插件</span><br>                  <span class="hljs-string">"@babel/preset-env"</span>,<br>                  { <span class="hljs-comment">// 配置信息</span><br>                    <span class="hljs-attr">targets</span>: {<br>                      <span class="hljs-string">"chrome"</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"58"</span>,<br>                      <span class="hljs-string">"ie"</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"11"</span>,<br>                    },<br>                    <span class="hljs-comment">// corejs版本</span><br>                    <span class="hljs-string">"corejs"</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"0"</span>,<br>                    <span class="hljs-comment">// 使用corejs的方式, usage表示按需加载</span><br>                    <span class="hljs-string">"useBuiltIns"</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"usage"</span><br>                  }<br>                ]<br>              ]<br>            }<br>          },<br>          <span class="hljs-string">'ts-loader'</span>,<br>        ],<br>        <span class="hljs-attr">exclude</span>: <span class="hljs-regexp">/node_modules/</span><br>      }<br>    ]<br>}<br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>设置打包文件的时候不时候箭头函数</p><p><img src="/2021/05/16/webpack%E6%89%93%E5%8C%85ts%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81/image-20210516163002278.png" alt="image-20210516163002278"></p></li><li><p>webpack打包css</p><p>安装依赖文件</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs js">npm i -D style-loader css-loader<br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>修改webpack.config.js</p><p><img src="/2021/05/16/webpack%E6%89%93%E5%8C%85ts%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81/image-20210516175735524.png" alt="image-20210516175735524"></p><p>引入css,不能在html中直接用,需要使用模块引入css到ts文件中</p><figure class="highlight typescript"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs typescript"><span class="hljs-comment">// index.ts</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> <span class="hljs-string">'./style.css'</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> typescript </tag>
            
            <tag> webpack </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>redux学习</title>
      <link href="2021/05/13/redux%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/"/>
      <url>2021/05/13/redux%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="相关概念"><a href="#相关概念" class="headerlink" title="相关概念"></a>相关概念</h2><h3 id="什么是Redux"><a href="#什么是Redux" class="headerlink" title="什么是Redux"></a>什么是Redux</h3><p><code>Redux</code>是Js状态容器</p><h3 id="什么是React绑定库"><a href="#什么是React绑定库" class="headerlink" title="什么是React绑定库"></a>什么是React绑定库</h3><p><code>Redux</code>是js状态容器,如果要在React中使用还需要安装<code>react-redux</code>,这个就是绑定库</p><h2 id="重点"><a href="#重点" class="headerlink" title="重点"></a>重点</h2><ul><li><p>应用中所有的<code>state</code>的以一个<strong>对象树</strong>的形式储存在一个单一的<code>store</code>中.</p></li><li><p>唯一改变<code>state</code>的办法是触发<code>action</code>,一个描述发生什么的对象</p></li><li><p>为了描述<code>action</code>如何改变state树,还需要<code>reduer</code></p></li></ul><h2 id="三大原则"><a href="#三大原则" class="headerlink" title="三大原则"></a>三大原则</h2><ol><li><p>所有state存在于一个对象树里,对象树存在于一个store中</p></li><li><p>state是只读的</p></li><li><p>使用纯函数来执行修改</p></li></ol><h2 id="使用"><a href="#使用" class="headerlink" title="使用"></a>使用</h2><h3 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h3><p>在react中使用还需要react-redux绑定库.</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs js">npm install react-redux<br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>安装redux</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs js">npm install redux<br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h3 id="引入"><a href="#引入" class="headerlink" title="引入"></a>引入</h3><p>创建store.js用来存放store,在store中,引入redux</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs js"><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> { createStore, combineReducers, applyMiddleware, compose } <span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> <span class="hljs-string">'redux'</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> createSagaMiddleware <span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> <span class="hljs-string">'redux-saga'</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> { put, takeEvery, call } <span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> <span class="hljs-string">'redux-saga/effects'</span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> saga = createSagaMiddleware()<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> initalState = { <span class="hljs-comment">/*初始state对象*/</span> }<br><span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> reduer1 = <span class="hljs-function">(<span class="hljs-params">state , action</span>) =&gt;</span> {<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">switch</span> (action.type) {<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">case</span> <span class="hljs-string">'ADD_TODO'</span> :<br>      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> {<br>        <span class="hljs-comment">/* 修改后的新的state */</span><br>      }<br>    <span class="hljs-attr">default</span>:<br>      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> state<br>  }<br>}<br><span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> reduer2 = <span class="hljs-function">(<span class="hljs-params">state , action</span>) =&gt;</span> {<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">switch</span> (action.type) {<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">case</span> <span class="hljs-string">'Visibility'</span> :<br>      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> {<br>        <span class="hljs-comment">/* 修改后的新的state */</span><br>      }<br>    <span class="hljs-attr">default</span>:<br>      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> state<br>  }<br>}<br><span class="hljs-comment">// 可以把不同的reduer合并为一个reduer</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> reduer = combineReducers({reduer1, reduer2})<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// 创建store</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> store = createStore(reducer, applyMiddleware(saga)<br>                     <br><span class="hljs-keyword">export</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">default</span> store<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> *<span class="hljs-title">getUserInfo</span>(<span class="hljs-params"></span>) </span>{<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">try</span> {<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> res = <span class="hljs-keyword">yield</span> axios.get(url)<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">yield</span> put({<span class="hljs-attr">type</span>: <span class="hljs-string">'XXX'</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">user</span>: res.data})<br>  } <span class="hljs-keyword">catch</span> {<br>  <br>  }<br>}<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> *<span class="hljs-title">rootSaga</span>(<span class="hljs-params"></span>) </span>{<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">yield</span> takeEvery(<span class="hljs-string">'get-user-info'</span>, getUserInfo)<br>}<br><br>saga.run(rootSaga)<br>                          <br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h3 id="问题"><a href="#问题" class="headerlink" title="问题"></a>问题</h3><h4 id="什么是redux-saga"><a href="#什么是redux-saga" class="headerlink" title="什么是redux-saga"></a>什么是redux-saga</h4><p>redux中用来处理异步的中间件插件,用于管理应用程序副作用.</p><p>使用了es6的Generator</p><h4 id="put-call的区别"><a href="#put-call的区别" class="headerlink" title="put,call的区别"></a>put,call的区别</h4><p><code>put</code>是根据类型调用reduer里面的修改.</p><p><code>call</code>是调用store里面的函数</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
